        <updateDate>2019-11-01T13:40:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Border Patrol Pay Security Act of 2019</strong></p> <p>This bill changes how border patrol agents receive overtime pay when working up to 100 hours in a two-week period. For hours worked above 80, an agent shall receive at least one and one-half times the agent's regular hourly rate. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
